flowchart TD
    Start([Tamu buka /chatbot]) --> Greet[Chatbot sapa user]
    Greet --> Intent{Intent message?}

    Intent -->|Pertanyaan informasi<br/>fasilitas, lokasi, kebijakan| InfoAns[Jawab dari knowledge base<br/>system prompt]
    InfoAns --> AskMore{Ada permintaan<br/>lanjutan?}
    AskMore -->|Ya| Intent
    AskMore -->|Tidak| End

    Intent -->|Cek ketersediaan / pesan kamar| CheckLogin{User<br/>logged in?}

    CheckLogin -->|Tidak| AskLogin[Pesan: 'Untuk reservasi<br/>silakan login dulu']
    AskLogin --> RedirLogin["/login"]
    RedirLogin --> End

    CheckLogin -->|Ya| HasGuestInfo{Sudah ada<br/>name email phone?}
    HasGuestInfo -->|Tidak| ShowGuestForm[Render SHOW_GUEST_FORM<br/>chatbot minta data]
    ShowGuestForm --> WaitGuest[Tunggu user submit form]
    WaitGuest --> HasGuestInfo
    HasGuestInfo -->|Ya| AskDates{Sudah ada<br/>check-in check-out?}

    AskDates -->|Tidak| ShowDateSelector[Render SHOW_DATE_SELECTOR]
    ShowDateSelector --> WaitDate[Tunggu user pilih tanggal]
    WaitDate --> AskDates
    AskDates -->|Ya| CallCek[Tool cekKetersediaan<br/>checkIn checkOut]

    CallCek --> Avail{Ada kamar<br/>tersedia?}
    Avail -->|Tidak| NoRooms[Pesan: tidak tersedia,<br/>tawarkan tanggal lain]
    NoRooms --> Intent
    Avail -->|Ya| ShowCards[Render ROOM_CARDS_JSON<br/>list kamar interaktif]

    ShowCards --> WaitPick[Tunggu user pilih kamar]
    WaitPick --> ConfirmDetail[Tampilkan ringkasan<br/>untuk konfirmasi]
    ConfirmDetail --> UserConfirm{User<br/>confirm?}
    UserConfirm -->|Tidak| Intent
    UserConfirm -->|Ya| CallCreate[Tool createBooking<br/>guest + room + dates]

    CallCreate --> SaveDB[(INSERT guests if new<br/>INSERT reservation<br/>status=confirmed<br/>payment=pending)]
    SaveDB --> ShowPay[Render SHOW_PAYMENT_OPTIONS<br/>Bank Transfer Card E-Wallet]

    ShowPay --> PayChoice{User pilih}
    PayChoice -->|Pay Now| InstrPay[Instruksi transfer<br/>BCA 7125348238]
    PayChoice -->|Pay Later| Pending[Status pending<br/>arahkan ke front office<br/>booking code DITAHAN]
    Pending --> End

    InstrPay --> WaitPaid[Tunggu user konfirmasi<br/>'sudah transfer']
    WaitPaid --> CallConfirm[Tool confirmPayment<br/>bookingReference]

    CallConfirm --> InsertPay[(INSERT payments<br/>UPDATE reservation<br/>payment_status=paid)]
    InsertPay --> Reveal[Reveal booking_reference<br/>+ instruksi check-in]
    Reveal --> End([Selesai])

    classDef startEnd fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#10b981
    classDef decision fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b
    classDef action fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6
    classDef llm fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#ec4899
    classDef db fill:#e0e7ff,stroke:#6366f1

    class Start,End startEnd
    class Intent,CheckLogin,HasGuestInfo,AskDates,Avail,UserConfirm,PayChoice,AskMore decision
    class Greet,InfoAns,AskLogin,RedirLogin,ShowGuestForm,WaitGuest,ShowDateSelector,WaitDate,NoRooms,ShowCards,WaitPick,ConfirmDetail,InstrPay,WaitPaid,Pending,ShowPay,Reveal action
    class CallCek,CallCreate,CallConfirm llm
    class SaveDB,InsertPay db
